&lt;p&gt;The brief was to take the dark courtyard and create a seating space with light for more of the day than the current yard offers, there are many other houses and trees around casting shadows that we realised we could mitigate by raising the seating area, a plan was formed to create a decking area above the replacement outhouse, the Cludgy being a name for a similar structure used by my Aunt.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Carvings</title><link>https://treebeardcreations.github.io/carving/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://treebeardcreations.github.io/carving/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A selection of carvings and other small random curiosities.&lt;/p&gt;



